WSN application based on R-CTP

****************************************************************************************************
* Programming the sink:

In the sink directory run:
	make iris
	make iris reinstall.1 mib520,/dev/ttyUSB* 
where * is the first usb port of the programming board (1 is the node ID for the sink)


****************************************************************************************************
* Programming the motes:

In the mote directory run:
	make micaz
	make micaz reinstall.id mib520,/dev/ttyUSB*
where * is the first usb port of the programming board and "id" is the node id.

** TelosB motes only have 1 USB port.
	make telosb
	make telosb reinstall.id bsl,/dev/ttyUSB*



